{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "慕容秋荻以假哭假打的方式栽赃谢晓峰，引来华少坤、谢凤凰、谢掌柜和娃娃等人作见证。谢凤凰以谢家家法\"戒淫\"之条要清理门户，欲拔剑惩治谢晓峰。谢掌柜突然出手，以谢家独门夺剑术夺下谢凤凰手中之剑，揭示自己是谢家老太爷远房堂侄的身份。华少坤令谢掌柜将剑归还谢晓峰，随后与妻子谢凤凰深情话别——二十年来他因败于谢晓峰剑下而郁郁，如今苦练木棍二十年，不惜冒死再战，只为替妻子争口气。最终华少坤解开黄布包袱，露出一根普通木棍作为武器，慕容秋荻暗自分析华少坤苦练二十年必有相当把握，赌他六四开甚至七三开的胜率。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你居然要我做这些事，你不是呆子谁是呆子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你说完了没有？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "说完了又怎么样？难道你想杀了我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好，你杀了我吧，你这么对我，反正我也不想活了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "喜欢你的女人太多，我知道你渐渐就会忘了我的，所以我每隔几年就要修理你一次，好让你永远忘不了我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么不索性痛痛快快的杀了我？为什么要这样打我？折磨我。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "娃娃。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "三少爷，好久不见了，你好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "你怎么会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们都是慕容姑娘请来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "她请你们来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "来看你做的好事。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "想不到我们谢家竟出了你这样的人才，不但会欺负女人，连自己的孩子都可以不要。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你已经骗了她两次，她还是全心全意的对你，你为什么还要把她打成这样子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "他……他没有……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你少开口，刚才你们在那小客栈里说的话，我们全都听得清清楚楚，他自己既然一句都不敢否认，你为什么还要替他洗脱？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "那些话谢掌柜是不是也全都听得清清楚楚？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说别的女人，我们管不着，也懒得管。可是姑苏慕容跟我们谢家的关系却不同，就是你不要你的儿子，我们谢家却不能不认这个孩子，更不能不认这个媳妇。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "谢家的家法第一条是什么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你既已犯了这一戒，就算我大哥护着你，我也容不得你！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我就要替我们谢家清理门户，你还不跪下来听命受刑！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "人证物证俱在，难道你还不肯认错，难道你敢不服家法？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "华夫人，请息怒！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "我想三少爷心里也许还有些不足为外人道的苦衷，就算华夫人要用家法处治他，也不妨先回去见了老太爷再说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "你口口声声的叫我华夫人，是不是想提醒我，我已不是谢家的人？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "小人不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "就算我已不是谢家的人，这把剑却还是谢家的剑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "这把剑就是家法。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "华夫人说得有理，只不过小人还有一点不明白。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "我不懂谢家的家法，怎么会到了华家人的手里？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "你好大的胆子，竟敢对姑奶奶无理。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "小人不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "你是从哪里学会这一招的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "华夫人既然也认出了这一招，那就最好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "这是老爷子的亲传，他老人家再三嘱咐我，学会了这一招后，千万不可乱用，可是只要看见谢家的剑在外姓人的手里，就一定要用这一招去夺回来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "老爷子说出来的话，我当然不敢不听。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "阁下是谢家的什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "算起来，小人只不过是老太爷的一个远房堂侄而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "你知道这把剑是什么剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "这就是谢家的祖宗传下来的四把宝剑之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "好剑！",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "的确是好剑！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "阁下配不配用这把剑？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "不配。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "text": "那么阁下为何还不将这把剑送还给三少爷？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_gui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "谢掌柜",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "小人正有此意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "再过几天，就是十一月十五了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "好像还要再过八天。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "到了那一天，你嫁给我就已有整整二十年。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "我记得。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "我从小就有个誓愿，一定要到成名后再成亲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "我成名时已四十出头，我娶你的时候，比你就整整大了二十岁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "现在你还是比我大二十岁。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "这二十年来，只有你知道我过的是什么样的日子。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "我知道，你……你一直觉得对不起我。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "因为我败了，我已不是娶你时那个华少坤，无论到了什么地方，都已没法子再出人头地，可是你……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "你从来也没有埋怨过，一直都在忍受着我的古怪脾气，没有你，我说不定早已死在阴沟里。",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "我为什么要埋怨你？这二十年，每天早上一醒来，就能看见你在我的身边，对一个女人来说，还有什么事能比得上这种福气？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "可是现在我已经老了，说不定哪天早上，你醒来时就会发现我已离你而去。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "每个人都迟早会有那么样一天的，这种事我一向看得很淡，可是我绝不能让别人说，谢家的姑奶奶，嫁的是个没出息的丈夫，我总要为你争口气！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "你真的明白？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我用的已不是剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "自从败在你剑下后，我已发誓终生不再用剑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这二十年来，我又练成了另外一种兵刃，我日日夜夜都在盼望着，能够再与你一战。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "speaker_name": "华少坤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是我已败在你剑下，败军之将，已不足言勇，所以你若不屑再与我这老人交手，我也不怪你。",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_feng_huang",
      "speaker_name": "谢凤凰",
      "listener": "char_hua_shao_kun",
      "text": "我来帮你的忙。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
